The '''Lastdark Club''' was an exclusive club in [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It was in the top floor of the world's tallest building, which was where it got its name: when the sun set, it was the last location to be in sunlight. [[Rostek Horn]] became a member in [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]] and supplied half the club's plant arrangements. Its decoration included [[Nerf/Legends|nerf]]-hide chairs and it offered [[Corellian brandy/Legends|Corellian brandy]].

